column4: NSLOCTEXT("[E773B63245369E4020C57EBDEE1D4273]", "C58598A94E08C1426C0CFE93B30B4F12", "I know all about you, but I didn\'t know you were a kid.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E773B63245369E4020C57EBDEE1D4273]", "CF824EA04608152AF8FD3EB740856853", "I can\'t believe a kid has been messing up my plan.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E773B63245369E4020C57EBDEE1D4273]", "D059693246E815673A0652B783160231", "I was so close to ruling the Net World.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E773B63245369E4020C57EBDEE1D4273]", "2572B64D4E3EE7625D72BAA7B3AE044A", "You\'re a grown up! Stop this, you\'re hurting everyone.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E773B63245369E4020C57EBDEE1D4273]", "9AA5192545A1589FECF11794622D4B32", "I don\'t care if I\'m hurting Digimon.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E773B63245369E4020C57EBDEE1D4273]", "D29262B4447E98E67F91CD97657FA6B2", "You\'re wrong! Digimon have hearts and minds! We\'re friends!")
NSLOCTEXT("[E773B63245369E4020C57EBDEE1D4273]", "6F96D1EB447FA99B89E08981B51594E3", "Let\'s fight and see if slaves or friends are better.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E773B63245369E4020C57EBDEE1D4273]", "AB44C7094453ADD23829C38778EDE87C", "If you leave the island alone and ask for forgiveness they will forgive you.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E773B63245369E4020C57EBDEE1D4273]", "09120A294B6D41FC0FDA9881F329C96F", "I shouldn\'t have trusted Digimon. I\'ll do it myself.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E773B63245369E4020C57EBDEE1D4273]", "3A0F652743D47EB8258F578CFD8D0B4C", "I\'m going to blow the island up and will escape to another world. Too bad kid!")
NSLOCTEXT("[E773B63245369E4020C57EBDEE1D4273]", "DA9621C947E19C3ACA8C99A6BECCDA8D", "I\'m sorry guys. There\'s nothing I can do now.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E773B63245369E4020C57EBDEE1D4273]", "BC0DC57B4CDBAA74396E29A3479430C0", "It\'s not transferring! Something is wrong in the program. What\'s happening?!")
NSLOCTEXT("[E773B63245369E4020C57EBDEE1D4273]", "4E3A0CDA4939CE07C19A228D51FC7054", "I can hear everyone\'s voices! Who is there?")
NSLOCTEXT("[E773B63245369E4020C57EBDEE1D4273]", "A7F09EA14F90505C056093BAF86BC726", "I am sending our energy to you right now.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E773B63245369E4020C57EBDEE1D4273]", "8EC92E3C458E2ED31DD7E8B3ED7263DD", "I guess we made it in time!")
NSLOCTEXT("[E773B63245369E4020C57EBDEE1D4273]", "B6F5F93C41B87A846018EA8D32059FFB", "No, this stupid thing! Help! Help me! Ahhhhhhh!!!")
